
Full documentation is at: https://github.com/difx/difx/wiki/vex2difx

Requirements:

vex2difx requires a recent version of difxio available within the same git repo as vex2difx:
https://github.com/difx/difx

To install from a fresh svn checkout, run the following:

aclocal
libtoolize --copy --force
autoconf
autoheader
automake -a

./configure --prefix=${DIFXROOT}
make
# (su root?)
make install

After an svn update, these steps do not need to be rerun.  at most, running 
autoreconf should be enough, but usually just "make" will update 
everything properly.

